**/private/
**/confidential/
credentials.md
personal-notes.md

# OS Files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor/IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.swn
*~
.project
.classpath
.settings/

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.cache
.cache/

